ercises for seniors.";i:4;s:116:"Practice these basic movements and choose one or two exercises from each category for a well-rounded seated workout.";i:5;s:66:"30 minute full body workout for seniors - seniors chair exercises.";i:6;s:115:"Join Mike Physiotherapist for this gentle seated 30-minute seated exercises for seniors which works the whole body.";i:7;s:50:"There is a quick break halfway through this video.";i:8;s:72:"If you need to have a break pause the video before you get back into it.";i:9;s:55:"Seniors 35-minute Chair Workout - Get stronger over 60.";i:10;s:106:"Join me Mike - Physiotherapist for this full chair workout covering exercises for every area of your body.";i:11;s:50:"Get stronger improve your flexibility and fitness.";i:12;s:24:"Move better feel better.";i:13;s:33:"This session goes for 35 minutes.";i:14;s:25:"In this Workout we cover.";i:15;s:41:"Chair yoga safely improves senior health.";i:16;s:88:"Chair yoga is a great way for older adults to get the wonderful health benefits of yoga.";i:17;s:101:"Staying seated means that even frail seniors or those who arent flexible can safely do the exercises.";i:18;s:56:"Chair exercises are a great substitute for aging adults.";i:19;s:117:"There doesnt need to be a weight set a trainer and seniors dont even have to have a caregiver with them at all times.";i:20;s:41:"The only thing a senior needs is a chair.";i:21;s:117:"Though some of the following exercises may require a resistance band or dumbbells to perform accurately with results.";i:22;s:70:"Gentle exercise 30 min video which includes floor work and stretching.";i:23;s:34:"Can be adapted for chair exercise.";i:24;s:63:"Designed to help everyone over 50 and over 60 and even over 70.";i:25;s:29:"Active Seniors Health Centre.";i:26;s:109:"Active Seniors specialises in seniors health focusing on exercise nutrition attitude and a healthy lifestyle.";i:27;s:25:"The worst core exercises.";i:28;s:98:"In the old days sit-ups and crunches were the go-to